Archetypal buddy cops Riggs (Mel Gibson) and Murtaugh (Danny Glover) are back for another round of high-stakes action, this time setting their collective sights on bringing down a former Los Angeles police lieutenant turned black market weapons dealer (Stuart Wilson). Rene Russo joins director Richard Donner's groundbreaking series as Lorna Cole, the beautiful yet hardnosed internal affairs sergeant who catches Riggs's eye.
