Lethal Weapon 4  (1998)  127 Minutes

In the combustible action franchise's final installment, maverick detectives Martin Riggs (Mel Gibson) and Roger Murtaugh (Danny Glover) square off against Asian mobster Wah Sing Ku (Jet Li), who's up to his neck in slave trading and counterfeit currency. With help from gumshoe Leo Getz (Joe Pesci) and smart-aleck rookie cop Lee Butters (Chris Rock), Riggs and Murtaugh aim to take down Ku and his gang. Rene Russo also stars.

